<blockquote>
<p>We are called the SCP Foundation. That’s Special Containment Procedures.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>It feels a bit awkward to me when people in-universe explicitly say &quot;We are called the Special Containment Procedures Foundation&quot; or the like. I guess being called &quot;just The Foundation&quot; or &quot;The SCP Foundation (don't ask what SCP stands for)&quot; may also be a bit odd when you think about it, but at least in a way where it isn't stated out loud.</p>
<p>Aside from that; I do dig little Tales like this, and it was pretty well done here. +1</p>

